# Learning rules

## Flashcards/SRS
- Cards may include text, furigana, examples, tags, audio/media references, and images.
- Image cards must support upload and provider-sourced candidate selection via abstraction.
- SRS logic must be deterministic and tested.

## BJT
- BJT quiz/exam content must support sections, skills, business scenarios, distractors, explanations, and analytics.
- Results should coach users, not shame them.

## Battle
- Battle must be realtime-ready via Socket.IO.
- Bot battles may come before full user-vs-user PvP.
- Fairness, abandonment, and bot tuning must be measurable.
